      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute beauty with you. This car has been my total pride and joy, and it\u2019s been kept in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by and see just how special this one is!",
