    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade A80 Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant with factory-spec sequential turbocharging. This example retains its original Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue, with all factory VIN tags present and a pristine undercarriage. Mechanically, the longitudinal iron-block engine maintains optimal compression across all cylinders, paired with a leak-free cooling system and an untouched wiring harness. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing the precise lateral grip and damping characteristics expected from a flagship grand tourer. Truly a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
