      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in concours-level condition and representing the pinnacle of its class. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Opportunities to acquire a specimen of this caliber are exceedingly rare.",
      "price": 46500.0,
