    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute favorite ride, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total dream! This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it shows in every single detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
