    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe (E92) in concours-level condition. Power is delivered by the legendary S65B40 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a screaming 8,400 RPM redline. This example features the 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip and driver engagement. The chassis remains taut with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system functioning perfectly across all damping profiles. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already performed. The Alpine White exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the Novillo leather interior shows zero bolster wear. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector seeking the pinnacle of high-revving atmospheric performance.",
